with Shen Xing?

283
00:13:57,977 --> 00:13:59,297
Our love's gone.

284
00:14:02,097 --> 00:14:02,736
Where's my wine?

285
00:14:10,977 --> 00:14:11,856
Sounds like a scum?

286
00:14:13,136 --> 00:14:15,776
That depends on how much
you took advantage of her.

287
00:14:16,016 --> 00:14:17,896
I didn't want to keep
taking advantage of her,

288
00:14:17,896 --> 00:14:19,817
so I wanted to end it quickly.

289
00:14:20,417 --> 00:14:21,496
Why be so hard on yourself?

290
00:14:22,536 --> 00:14:24,808
Feel ashamed about being supported
by your father-in-law?

291
00:14:25,057 --> 00:14:25,776
No.

292
00:14:26,016 --> 00:14:28,217
Having someone to support me
is pleasant.

293
00:14:31,977 --> 00:14:32,616
Really?

294
00:14:32,896 --> 00:14:33,457
Really.

295
00:14:34,016 --> 00:14:35,376
Only those who've been in it know,

296
00:14:35,896 --> 00:14:36,656
like me.

297
00:14:38,896 --> 00:14:40,577
Then you should hold on to it.

298
00:14:41,217 --> 00:14:42,297
I can't.

299
00:14:43,977 --> 00:14:44,577
Why?

300
00:14:45,776 --> 00:14:47,676
Who can stand their girlfriend

301
00:14:47,752 --> 00:14:49,736
celebrating another man's birthday
now and then?

302
00:14:51,016 --> 00:14:52,736
A wise man knows when to yield.

303
00:14:52,736 --> 00:14:53,856
Endure it for your future.

304
00:14:54,337 --> 00:14:55,136
Just like you?

305
00:14:58,616 --> 00:14:59,177
What?

306
00:14:59,656 --> 00:15:02,417
Haven't you been standing your husband
being with other women,

307
00:15:02,656 --> 00:15:03,912
acting like nothing happened?

308
00:15:04,457 --> 00:15:05,616
Is it for your future too?

309
00:15:16,856 --> 00:15:18,496
Zhao Mei, wait.

310
00:15:18,496 --> 00:15:19,097
Let go!

311
00:15:19,097 --> 00:15:20,376
Sorry. My apologies.

312
00:15:21,337 --> 00:15:22,656
Yes, I might disgust you.

313
00:15:23,337 --> 00:15:25,376
I don't even know how to explain...

314
00:15:25,736 --> 00:15:27,016
Y-You came to apologize to me.

315
00:15:27,016 --> 00:15:27,977
I should be grateful.

316
00:15:27,977 --> 00:15:28,656
I'm grateful.

317
00:15:28,656 --> 00:15:30,417
But I don't know why

318
00:15:30,417 --> 00:15:31,417
I wanted to provoke you.

319
00:15:31,417 --> 00:15:32,376
Stay away from me.

320
00:15:34,937 --> 00:15:35,656
Zhao Mei, sorry.

321
00:15:35,656 --> 00:15:36,616
I shouldn't say that.

322
00:15:36,896 --> 00:15:37,616
I don't know why.

323
00:15:37,616 --> 00:15:39,016
But my mind is just a mess today.

324
00:15:39,016 --> 00:15:40,376
I don't know why I said so to you.

325
00:15:40,376 --> 00:15:41,337
Please forgive me.

326
00:15:42,136 --> 00:15:43,776
I didn't mean it, Zhao Mei.

327
00:15:44,217 --> 00:15:45,457
Zhao Mei, forgive me.

328
00:15:45,736 --> 00:15:46,496
Fine. Listen,

329
00:15:46,496 --> 00:15:47,256
I resigned.

330
00:15:49,616 --> 00:15:50,496
You resigned?

331
00:15:51,496 --> 00:15:53,097
What does that have to do with me?

332
00:15:53,536 --> 00:15:54,616
So what then?

333
00:15:54,977 --> 00:15:56,656
Does it give you the right
to humiliate me?

334
00:15:56,656 --> 00:15:58,097
It has something to do with you.

335
00:16:01,217 --> 00:16:02,656
Fine. It has nothing to do with you.

336
00:16:03,016 --> 00:16:05,417
I resigned because you won
the competition between us.

337
00:16:07,256 --> 00:16:08,016
As a man,

338
00:16:08,016 --> 00:16:09,896
I didn't want to win because of a dog.

339
00:16:19,256 --> 00:16:23,376
That dog was part
of Shen Mo's setup, wasn't it?

340
00:16:30,656 --> 00:16:31,256
It's raining.

341
00:16:32,977 --> 00:16:34,376
Let's take shelter from rain.

342
00:17:29,536 --> 00:17:30,856
Why not change your clothes?

343
00:17:32,377 --> 00:17:33,816
I don't have spare clothes.

344
00:17:35,576 --> 00:17:37,056
I have a hairdryer. Want to dry off?

345
00:17:38,377 --> 00:17:38,897
Right there.

346
00:17:45,096 --> 00:17:46,457
You really have everything here.

347
00:17:46,657 --> 00:17:47,776
You could even live here.

348
00:17:47,776 --> 00:17:49,496
Stop talking and just dry it.

349
00:17:49,496 --> 00:17:50,376
Or you'd catch a cold.

350
00:18:10,937 --> 00:18:11,496
Done drying.

351
00:18:12,177 --> 00:18:12,736
What's wrong?

352
00:18:13,056 --> 00:18:14,056
I was drying my hair,

353
00:18:14,217 --> 00:18:15,296
and you're drinking,

354
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:17,928
it feels like you had
done something to me.

355
00:18:18,016 --> 00:18:18,617
Pathetic.

356
00:18:28,336 --> 00:18:29,137
Shut up!

357
00:18:29,217 --> 00:18:30,096
Okay, fine.

358
00:18:49,736 --> 00:18:50,816
Your back is soaked.

359
00:18:51,137 --> 00:18:51,897
I'll help you.

360
00:18:54,016 --> 00:18:54,617
Be gentle.

361
00:18:54,617 --> 00:18:55,417
Drop dead.

362
00:19:12,736 --> 00:19:15,617
I've already asked Li Dongming
for a divorce.

363
00:19:21,336 --> 00:19:21,937
What?

364
00:19:24,177 --> 00:19:24,776
Divorce?

365
00:19:26,897 --> 00:19:29,977
At first, I thought I could stand it.

366
00:19:32,137 --> 00:19:33,416
But later I realized

367
00:19:36,936 --> 00:19:38,096
I couldn't.

368
00:19:41,496 --> 00:19:42,536
Quite ridiculous.

369
00:20:12,937 --> 00:20:13,736
I'm going home.

370
00:20:25,544 --> 00:20:27,272
Mr. Dong, Shen Mo
suddenly had an attack.

371
00:20:27,272 --> 00:20:29,032
He's in emergency treatment
in the hospital.

372
00:20:29,032 --> 00:20:30,152
I can't handle it alone.

373
00:20:30,256 --> 00:20:32,056
But I don't have Shen Xing's contact.

374
00:20:32,177 --> 00:20:32,857
On my way now.

375
00:20:34,496 --> 00:20:35,056
How is he?

376
00:20:35,056 --> 00:20:35,617
Mr. Dong.

377
00:20:37,056 --> 00:20:37,897
He's stabilized.

378
00:20:39,296 --> 00:20:41,336
He was scheduled for surgery
in a couple of days.

379
00:20:41,457 --> 00:20:44,697
But he suddenly saw
that video of Shen Xing,

380
00:20:44,697 --> 00:20:46,056
so his blood pressure spiked.

381
00:20:46,617 --> 00:20:48,657
Fortunately, he got emergency treatment.

382
00:20:49,617 --> 00:20:51,697
I didn't know
his blood pressure was that high.

383
00:20:51,937 --> 00:20:53,697
Despite that, he still drinks every day?

384
00:20:53,776 --> 00:20:55,177
He's really got a death wish.

385
00:20:55,296 --> 00:20:56,736
Who is the patient's family member?

386
00:20:57,217 --> 00:20:58,056
Doctor, hello.

387
00:20:58,096 --> 00:20:59,177
His daughter is on her way.

388
00:20:59,177 --> 00:21:00,096
You can talk to me.

389
00:21:00,417 --> 00:21:02,056
The patient's condition is stable now.

390
00:21:02,336 --> 00:21:03,536
Come to my office first.

391
00:21:04,417 --> 00:21:06,736
Doctor, can I go see him?

392
00:21:07,096 --> 00:21:07,617
Yes.

393
00:21:07,617 --> 00:21:09,377
But don't disturb his rest.

394
00:21:09,857 --> 00:21:10,536
Okay, thank you.

395
00:21:33,776 --> 00:21:34,977
Don't talk now.

396
00:21:35,617 --> 00:21:36,776
Rest well.

397
00:21:50,336 --> 00:21:51,417
I'm here with you.

398
00:21:52,657 --> 00:21:53,256
Just sleep.

399
00:22:04,377 --> 00:22:05,576
He's asleep.

400
00:22:18,816 --> 00:22:19,617
You go back.

401
00:22:19,736 --> 00:22:20,776
Your kid needs you.

402
00:22:20,816 --> 00:22:21,377
I'll stay.

403
00:22:26,617 --> 00:22:27,617
I'll leave it to you.

404
00:22:27,617 --> 00:22:29,016
I'll find him a caregiver tomorrow.

405
00:22:29,256 --> 00:22:29,776
Go.

406
00:23:18,776 --> 00:23:22,576
You're awake. Your vital signs
have just stabilized.

407
00:23:22,697 --> 00:23:23,977
Get more rest.

408
00:23:25,496 --> 00:23:26,096
Mr. Shen.

409
00:23:29,576 --> 00:23:30,937
What are you doing here?

410
00:23:31,857 --> 00:23:32,937
He came last night.

411
00:23:33,217 --> 00:23:34,217
He stayed here all night.

412
00:23:35,536 --> 00:23:37,296
I told Liang Danning
to go home last night.

413
00:23:37,776 --> 00:23:38,897
You were stabilized.

414
00:23:38,897 --> 00:23:39,816
And she was exhausted.

415
00:23:40,937 --> 00:23:42,016
Thank you.

416
00:23:43,096 --> 00:23:44,377
And thank her too.

417
00:23:44,617 --> 00:23:45,496
Breakfast is ready.

418
00:23:45,536 --> 00:23:46,377
Get you a serving?

419
00:23:46,617 --> 00:23:47,296
I'll pass.

420
00:23:47,296 --> 00:23:48,256
Can't eat at this hour.

421
00:23:49,617 --> 00:23:51,736
He usually doesn't sleep
until this time.

422
00:23:52,096 --> 00:23:53,977
Right, but it's a bad habit.

423
00:23:54,377 --> 00:23:55,217
Needed to change.

424
00:23:56,377 --> 00:23:57,736
Are you hinting at me?

425
00:24:02,536 --> 00:24:05,256
(Hetai Center)

426
00:24:09,816 --> 00:24:10,776
Do you know

427
00:24:11,816 --> 00:24:15,457
what I'm thinking about right now?

428
00:24:17,056 --> 00:24:19,536
I'm thinking
that once I get out of here,

429
00:24:20,857 --> 00:24:24,056
I'll throw a huge banquet,
invite everyone,

430
00:24:24,857 --> 00:24:28,457
party wildly, and drink
for three days and nights straight.

431
00:24:29,256 --> 00:24:30,336
No one leaves sober.

432
00:24:33,056 --> 00:24:36,536
I'll block everyone who tells me
to live a healthy lifestyle.

433
00:24:39,177 --> 00:24:40,456
What's the point of living long?

434
00:24:42,016 --> 00:24:43,776
If I can't enjoy life, why live?

435
00:24:45,816 --> 00:24:46,952
Don't you talk me out of it?

436
00:24:47,496 --> 00:24:48,296
It's useless.

437
00:24:49,617 --> 00:24:51,977
If I could talk you out of it easily,
you wouldn't be you.

438
00:24:53,377 --> 00:24:53,897
Exactly.

439
00:24:56,256 --> 00:24:59,377
Do you know why I wanted
to marry Shen Xing off to you?

440
00:25:00,377 --> 00:25:01,857
Not because I particularly like you.

441
00:25:04,576 --> 00:25:06,857
In fact,
I really dislike people like you.

442
00:25:08,536 --> 00:25:10,016
If I were choosing a buddy,

443
00:25:11,457 --> 00:25:12,657
I wouldn't pick you.

444
00:25:14,377 --> 00:25:14,816
Why?

445
00:25:16,657 --> 00:25:17,697
You're too soft.

446
00:25:19,137 --> 00:25:21,137
Can't be ruthless when you need to be.

447
00:25:21,657 --> 00:25:23,496
Hesitate to act when action is required.

448
00:25:24,296 --> 00:25:25,576
You'll never amount to much.

449
00:25:31,897 --> 00:25:34,336
But choosing a son-in-law
isn't picking a buddy.

450
00:25:35,457 --> 00:25:37,736
I don't want my daughter
to end up with someone like me.

451
00:25:40,897 --> 00:25:41,937
You're a smart person.

452
00:25:43,137 --> 00:25:44,296
I won't beat around the bush.

453
00:25:46,096 --> 00:25:48,417
I have all these assets,

454
00:25:49,937 --> 00:25:51,256
but I only have one daughter.

455
00:25:53,857 --> 00:25:55,336
She might not be very accomplished,

456
00:25:56,536 --> 00:25:59,016
but her love for you is genuine.

457
00:26:01,776 --> 00:26:02,776
Even though she acts out,

458
00:26:03,937 --> 00:26:06,697
it's ultimately because
she's been upset since the breakup.

459
00:26:07,977 --> 00:26:08,897
I'll say it again.

460
00:26:09,776 --> 00:26:11,496
If you marry Shen Xing,

461
00:26:12,536 --> 00:26:15,776
I'll give you everything I own.

462
00:26:16,937 --> 00:26:17,736
What do you think?

463
00:26:21,776 --> 00:26:22,897
Still reject me?

464
00:26:24,897 --> 00:26:25,937
I don't love Shen Xing.

465
00:26:27,417 --> 00:26:28,177
Here you go again.

466
00:26:30,016 --> 00:26:32,256
Shen Xing might not
truly love me either.

467
00:26:33,937 --> 00:26:37,336
It could be some possessiveness.

468
00:26:39,217 --> 00:26:40,137
I don't really know.

469
00:26:41,296 --> 00:26:44,056
But making her marry me
under these circumstances

470
00:26:45,857 --> 00:26:46,776
is not fair to her,

471
00:26:49,177 --> 00:26:50,536
even a kind of harm to her.

472
00:26:53,897 --> 00:26:54,857
I believe

473
00:26:56,816 --> 00:27:01,096
she'll find a man
better suited for her someday.

474
00:27:05,137 --> 00:27:05,897
I'm not worthy.

475
00:27:09,336 --> 00:27:10,296
But anyway,

476
00:27:10,296 --> 00:27:13,697
Mr. Shen, my respect
for you won't change.

477
00:27:14,697 --> 00:27:15,377
Do you know?

478
00:27:17,417 --> 00:27:18,697
Without my support,

479
00:27:19,897 --> 00:27:22,336
being Sales Director
won't be easy for you.

480
00:27:24,137 --> 00:27:25,217
I've already resigned.

481
00:27:27,617 --> 00:27:29,336
What? You...

482
00:27:29,457 --> 00:27:30,056
Mr. Shen,

483
00:27:30,897 --> 00:27:32,617
I've worked hard in Guangzhou for years.

484
00:27:33,657 --> 00:27:34,576
I drank so much.

485
00:27:37,336 --> 00:27:41,416
I really wanted that promotion
and to get that position,

486
00:27:42,792 --> 00:27:45,256
replacing Mr. Xu, desperately.

487
00:27:47,056 --> 00:27:49,937
But when I saw Mr. Xu get taken down,

488
00:27:51,776 --> 00:27:52,857
I didn't feel that happy.

489
00:27:55,457 --> 00:27:57,177
Instead, a voice inside me said,

490
00:27:57,177 --> 00:27:58,937
"You can't be Sales Director."

491
00:28:01,137 --> 00:28:05,536
"If you do, you'll become
the next Xu Yuntian."

492
00:28:06,576 --> 00:28:07,776
After what happened since,

493
00:28:09,137 --> 00:28:09,857
I understand now

494
00:28:11,256 --> 00:28:16,617
I can't, and I don't want
to become Xu Yuntian.

495
00:28:21,816 --> 00:28:22,576
Put that aside.

496
00:28:25,137 --> 00:28:26,296
You need to rest properly.

497
00:28:37,977 --> 00:28:40,056
I can't believe Dong Yue resigned.

498
00:28:40,136 --> 00:28:41,857
He was only in that position
for a few days.

499
00:28:41,857 --> 00:28:42,937
Less than a week, I guess.

500
00:28:43,417 --> 00:28:44,256
Right.

501
00:28:44,617 --> 00:28:47,137
Just three days total, I think.

502
00:28:48,816 --> 00:28:52,296
Has he found
a better position elsewhere?

503
00:28:52,296 --> 00:28:53,336
Definitely.

504
00:28:53,496 --> 00:28:54,296
Or he's crazy.

505
00:28:54,697 --> 00:28:55,857
Or he changed careers.

506
00:28:56,377 --> 00:28:58,127
GST pays the highest salary

507
00:28:58,127 --> 00:29:00,056
for Sales Directors in our industry,
doesn't it?

508
00:29:00,056 --> 00:29:01,697
Maybe he's dating a rich lady.

509
00:29:02,137 --> 00:29:02,977
Probably.

510
00:29:03,336 --> 00:29:04,736
Anyway, he just has good luck.

511
00:29:04,736 --> 00:29:05,776
Not like us.

512
00:29:06,657 --> 00:29:07,776
Then where does he go?

513
00:29:08,417 --> 00:29:09,177
Who knows?

514
00:29:09,897 --> 00:29:10,977
Revise this.

515
00:29:11,137 --> 00:29:11,576
Okay.

516
00:29:26,617 --> 00:29:28,096
Ms. Zhao, you wanted to see me?

517
00:29:29,256 --> 00:29:29,736
Have a seat.

518
00:29:31,776 --> 00:29:33,177
I ordered you an Americano.

519
00:29:35,816 --> 00:29:37,256
Why do you want to see me?

520
00:29:44,697 --> 00:29:47,937
You took that photo
of me and Dong Yue, didn't you?

521
00:29:55,137 --> 00:29:55,857
You knew that?

522
00:30:00,096 --> 00:30:02,897
Actually, I saw you and Dong Yue
go upstairs together that night.

523
00:30:05,137 --> 00:30:06,617
Why would you do that?

524
00:30:07,137 --> 00:30:08,736
Because I think you're hypocritical.

525
00:30:10,496 --> 00:30:12,056
Xu Yuntian harassed me,

526
00:30:12,056 --> 00:30:13,377
then you fired me.

527
00:30:13,937 --> 00:30:15,336
But you're not clean either.

528
00:30:16,296 --> 00:30:19,177
Look at your ambiguous relationship
with Hao.

529
00:30:19,617 --> 00:30:20,977
And you're involved with Dong Yue.

530
00:30:21,617 --> 00:30:23,816
You've got even more history
with Xu Yuntian, right?

531
00:30:24,937 --> 00:30:26,657
What right did you have to fire me?

532
00:30:29,457 --> 00:30:33,296
Do you think just because
you brought me back to GST,

533
00:30:33,296 --> 00:30:35,016
I should be grateful to you?

534
00:30:35,937 --> 00:30:37,977
No, you're wrong.

535
00:30:39,016 --> 00:30:40,016
I know perfectly well

536
00:30:40,857 --> 00:30:43,857
you've just used me as a pawn
from start to finish.

537
00:30:44,457 --> 00:30:45,576
Not just me.

538
00:30:46,137 --> 00:30:48,377
You treat everyone under you as a pawn.

539
00:30:48,816 --> 00:30:50,736
When you need them, you sweet talk them.

540
00:30:51,137 --> 00:30:52,617
When you don't, you kick them aside.

541
00:30:53,657 --> 00:30:54,776
I don't think that way.

542
00:30:54,776 --> 00:30:55,937
But you do exactly this way.

543
00:30:57,496 --> 00:30:59,137
Hao took the blame for you.

544
00:30:59,617 --> 00:31:01,296
He said he did it voluntarily.

545
00:31:01,617 --> 00:31:03,377
But he was just being used by you.

546
00:31:06,576 --> 00:31:08,177
You know quite a lot.

547
00:31:08,177 --> 00:31:09,137
And Fang.

548
00:31:10,096 --> 00:31:11,857
She was beaten so badly.

549
00:31:12,056 --> 00:31:14,217
Didn't you claim to be close to her?

550
00:31:14,776 --> 00:31:16,576
You didn't even visit her once.

551
00:31:19,056 --> 00:31:20,776
All you did was
to transfer her 2,000 yuan,

552
00:31:20,776 --> 00:31:22,177
then you disappeared.

553
00:31:22,937 --> 00:31:24,056
I was too swamped.

554
00:31:25,776 --> 00:31:26,857
How is she doing now?

555
00:31:26,857 --> 00:31:28,016
She went back to her hometown

556
00:31:28,377 --> 00:31:29,776
and would never come back.

557
00:31:30,937 --> 00:31:31,937
When did she leave?

558
00:31:32,137 --> 00:31:33,377
Stop pretending, okay?

559
00:31:34,096 --> 00:31:36,217
Stop acting like you care about her.

560
00:31:36,217 --> 00:31:37,137
You don't.

561
00:31:37,137 --> 00:31:38,857
You only care about yourself.

562
00:31:40,857 --> 00:31:45,096
So... So even though
you brought me back to GST,

563
00:31:45,576 --> 00:31:46,736
I'm not grateful at all.

564
00:31:47,417 --> 00:31:48,617
I'm not as foolish as Hao.

565
00:31:49,617 --> 00:31:51,296
I didn't expect your gratitude.

566
00:31:51,857 --> 00:31:53,937
Nor did I treat you as a pawn.

567
00:31:55,217 --> 00:31:57,377
To me, you're just a colleague.

568
00:32:00,177 --> 00:32:00,897
Zixuan.

569
00:32:02,096 --> 00:32:04,377
You've been working
for too short a time.

570
00:32:04,617 --> 00:32:06,177
With more experience, you'll realize

571
00:32:06,816 --> 00:32:10,496
quitting, joining, and promotions,
are like moving house,

572
00:32:10,857 --> 00:32:12,417
just some ordinary things in the world.

573
00:32:16,056 --> 00:32:18,256
However, I have to admit

574
00:32:20,056 --> 00:32:20,977
I misjudged you.

575
00:32:23,096 --> 00:32:27,177
It was you who told me the only way
to change my fate is to rely on myself.

576
00:32:27,697 --> 00:32:30,457
Otherwise, I'm only fit
to be used as a pawn,

577
00:32:30,457 --> 00:32:33,377
I only deserve to be
with a man like Lin Xiaosen,

578
00:32:33,377 --> 00:32:36,256
and I only deserve to be pushed
into the arms of powerful men.

579
00:32:37,536 --> 00:32:39,977
No, I don't want that.

580
00:32:40,897 --> 00:32:42,496
I will change my fate.

581
00:32:43,617 --> 00:32:46,457
And I'll make you experience
how I felt when I was cyberbullied.

582
00:32:49,457 --> 00:32:52,016
So, after all you've done,

583
00:32:53,336 --> 00:32:54,417
you want revenge on me.

584
00:32:54,576 --> 00:32:56,816
No, I'm here to tell you

585
00:32:57,336 --> 00:32:59,336
that although
we're just regular promoters,

586
00:32:59,336 --> 00:33:02,897
we also work diligently day and night

587
00:33:02,897 --> 00:33:04,377
and fight tooth and nail

588
00:33:04,377 --> 00:33:06,217
for the company and products.

589
00:33:06,617 --> 00:33:08,897
Why do you guys
get promotions and raises?

590
00:33:08,897 --> 00:33:10,536
Why can you guys climb the ladder?

591
00:33:10,697 --> 00:33:12,977
And we're doomed to never get ahead?

592
00:33:12,977 --> 00:33:14,897
Many years passed,
and we're still promoters.

593
00:33:14,897 --> 00:33:15,776
It's not fair.

594
00:33:20,857 --> 00:33:21,816
You've gotten ahead.

595
00:33:22,217 --> 00:33:26,096
Right, but at what cost?

596
00:33:26,336 --> 00:33:28,680
(I can't deny Zeng Zixuan stunned me.)

597
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:31,528
(For the first time, I was stunned
by someone so much younger than me)

598
00:33:31,528 --> 00:33:33,352
- (and far below me in rank.)
- Actually, I prefer lattes.

599
00:33:34,296 --> 00:33:35,657
(It made me a bit unsettled.)

600
00:33:36,617 --> 00:33:37,937
(Actually, I lied.)

601
00:33:38,417 --> 00:33:40,857
(I said I never expected
gratitude from those below me.)

602
00:33:40,857 --> 00:33:41,816
(How is that possible?)

603
00:33:42,177 --> 00:33:44,096
(Of course, I expected for it a little.)

604
00:33:44,536 --> 00:33:46,377
(I trained them and promoted them.)

605
00:33:46,377 --> 00:33:48,336
(I deserve some credit, don't I?)

606
00:33:49,736 --> 00:33:53,016
(The most horrible thing is,
I think she's right.)

607
00:33:59,240 --> 00:34:01,064
(Hetai Center)

608
00:34:06,576 --> 00:34:07,377
Ms. Liang.

609
00:34:08,337 --> 00:34:09,737
I need to talk to you.

610
00:34:10,696 --> 00:34:13,897
Mr. Shen just got out of emergency care
and he's already hosting guests.

611
00:34:13,937 --> 00:34:15,176
He still needs surgery.

612
00:34:15,176 --> 00:34:16,136
Can you talk to him?

613
00:34:16,136 --> 00:34:16,977
Okay, I'll do it.

614
00:34:19,377 --> 00:34:20,536
In that case,

615
00:34:20,656 --> 00:34:22,656
you've decided to be with Liang Danning?

616
00:34:23,457 --> 00:34:24,616
Not really.

617
00:34:26,417 --> 00:34:27,377
I'm still assessing her.

618
00:34:28,897 --> 00:34:29,656
You know very well

619
00:34:30,417 --> 00:34:35,616
guys like us are always suspicious
towards women.

620
00:34:36,696 --> 00:34:38,297
But Liang Danning is different.

621
00:34:39,576 --> 00:34:42,377
She has this sense of loyalty,

622
00:34:43,297 --> 00:34:46,496
genuinely no less than
what we had back in the day.

623
00:34:48,457 --> 00:34:50,096
Look at how she treats her bestie

624
00:34:50,696 --> 00:34:52,016
and her ex-husband.

625
00:34:52,897 --> 00:34:54,897
Her ex-husband was a hopeless gambler.

626
00:34:55,897 --> 00:34:57,897
At first, she didn't divorce him

627
00:34:57,897 --> 00:34:59,112
and helped pay off his debts.

628
00:35:00,337 --> 00:35:01,897
She really is a good woman.

629
00:35:02,777 --> 00:35:03,417
Yes.

630
00:35:04,096 --> 00:35:07,377
Before my surgery, I came clean to her.

631
00:35:09,257 --> 00:35:09,977
I said, "I'm old,"

632
00:35:11,576 --> 00:35:12,680
"suffering from illness."

633
00:35:14,576 --> 00:35:15,536
"But I like you."

634
00:35:16,536 --> 00:35:18,297
"Are you willing to be with me?"

635
00:35:19,536 --> 00:35:20,536
Did she agree?

636
00:35:22,136 --> 00:35:25,096
No, not yet.

637
00:35:25,977 --> 00:35:26,937
But that's good.

638
00:35:28,016 --> 00:35:29,817
It shows she's seriously
thinking about it.

639
00:35:30,777 --> 00:35:34,737
If she'd agreed right away,
I wouldn't have believed her.

640
00:35:35,897 --> 00:35:36,977
You're absolutely right.

641
00:35:37,536 --> 00:35:41,297
Mr. Shen, you are really
discerning in people.

642
00:35:46,176 --> 00:35:47,257
You're so lucky.

643
00:35:47,937 --> 00:35:48,937
I'm not as lucky as you.

644
00:35:49,656 --> 00:35:50,977
You know my wife,

645
00:35:51,417 --> 00:35:52,897
so scheming.

646
00:35:53,817 --> 00:35:54,696
I'm worrying

647
00:35:54,696 --> 00:35:56,937
that when I'm bedridden someday,

648
00:35:57,176 --> 00:35:58,656
she'll just pull the plug on me.

649
00:36:07,817 --> 00:36:08,696
Ms. Liang.

650
00:36:09,136 --> 00:36:09,536
Hi.

651
00:36:09,536 --> 00:36:10,417
I won't disturb you.

652
00:36:10,417 --> 00:36:11,056
You chat.

653
00:36:23,817 --> 00:36:25,297
Guess what I brought you?

654
00:36:26,136 --> 00:36:26,656
Wine?

655
00:36:27,616 --> 00:36:28,977
In your dreams!

656
00:36:30,696 --> 00:36:31,377
Look.

657
00:36:39,576 --> 00:36:40,680
Where did you find them?

658
00:36:41,016 --> 00:36:43,056
I found them in the company archives.

659
00:36:43,056 --> 00:36:45,096
I saw you were in them,
so I printed them out.

660
00:36:45,777 --> 00:36:47,216
I don't even have these photos.

661
00:36:48,897 --> 00:36:50,096
I remember this one.

662
00:36:50,337 --> 00:36:53,737
It was from a GST dinner
at the British Museum.

663
00:36:54,977 --> 00:36:57,136
Such great treatment!
How come I missed out?

664
00:36:57,696 --> 00:36:59,216
And this one was in Italy.

665
00:36:59,696 --> 00:37:02,297
I was with GST at a skiing competition.

666
00:37:02,496 --> 00:37:03,536
Italy!

667
00:37:04,337 --> 00:37:07,777
And this one's
from the GST Golf Masters.

668
00:37:14,616 --> 00:37:15,977
Is this Xu Yuntian?

669
00:37:16,377 --> 00:37:17,656
Yeah, that's him!

670
00:37:18,417 --> 00:37:20,096
He wasn't even thirty yet.

671
00:37:20,897 --> 00:37:22,056
Kind of handsome.

672
00:37:22,176 --> 00:37:23,337
Yes.

673
00:37:23,696 --> 00:37:24,897
Back then at GST,

674
00:37:26,176 --> 00:37:27,377
the men were handsome,

675
00:37:28,216 --> 00:37:29,417
and the women were beautiful.

676
00:37:31,977 --> 00:37:33,857
Alright then, I'll let you be. I'm off.

677
00:37:34,777 --> 00:37:35,624
Where are you going?

678
00:37:36,136 --> 00:37:38,297
I'm hosting the dinner tonight.

679
00:37:39,656 --> 00:37:40,656
The doctor told you,

680
00:37:40,656 --> 00:37:41,576
no more hosting guests.

681
00:37:41,576 --> 00:37:42,472
Or he'll make you pay.

682
00:37:44,496 --> 00:37:44,897
Bye.

683
00:37:48,897 --> 00:37:51,056
Did Dong Yue resign?

684
00:37:53,096 --> 00:37:53,496
Yes.

685
00:38:01,897 --> 00:38:03,697
Based on submissions
from all departments

686
00:38:03,697 --> 00:38:05,696
and the finance team's consolidation,

687
00:38:07,016 --> 00:38:09,977
if we can cut company spending
by another ten percent,

688
00:38:11,096 --> 00:38:12,296
we'll be profitable this year.

689
00:38:13,777 --> 00:38:17,176
And manpower is the biggest chunk
of company spending.

690
00:38:20,897 --> 00:38:21,737
Then fire some.

691
00:38:22,696 --> 00:38:24,337
This is too soon after the last one.

692
00:38:24,777 --> 00:38:26,717
During the last layoffs, you said

693
00:38:26,717 --> 00:38:28,857
it was just the first step
of structural optimization,

694
00:38:29,297 --> 00:38:30,496
kind of a notice in advance.

695
00:38:33,337 --> 00:38:33,857
Mr. Fan.

696
00:38:33,857 --> 00:38:36,056
Sorry to interrupt.
I need Mr. Xiao for something.

697
00:38:36,297 --> 00:38:37,737
Mr. Xiao, could you come with me?

698
00:38:38,536 --> 00:38:39,457
Security notified me

699
00:38:39,457 --> 00:38:42,576
that the system shows Qiao Hailun
hasn't left the office in 52 hours.

700
00:38:42,777 --> 00:38:43,777
That long? Are you sure?

701
00:38:44,008 --> 00:38:45,897
Yes. Clocking in and out
requires swiping cards.

702
00:38:45,897 --> 00:38:46,857
She hasn't swiped it

703
00:38:46,857 --> 00:38:47,848
and didn't answer calls.

704
00:38:48,377 --> 00:38:49,096
Anyone saw her?

705
00:38:49,096 --> 00:38:49,576
This way.

706
00:38:50,176 --> 00:38:50,817
I've asked.

707
00:38:51,096 --> 00:38:54,096
They said the last time she was seen
around 10 PM last night.

708
00:39:01,896 --> 00:39:02,920
Checked the surveillance?

709
00:39:03,208 --> 00:39:04,737
Needs to ask the property management

710
00:39:04,737 --> 00:39:06,568
and a formal application
with company seal.

711
00:39:06,568 --> 00:39:08,576
I'm afraid it'll cause a big stir.

712
00:39:10,136 --> 00:39:11,377
Send people to look for her.

713
00:39:11,536 --> 00:39:12,817
If we can't find her in an hour,

714
00:39:12,817 --> 00:39:14,297
apply for the surveillance footage.

715
00:39:14,297 --> 00:39:14,857
Okay.

716
00:39:23,377 --> 00:39:23,937
Qiao Hailun!

717
00:39:25,417 --> 00:39:26,257
Qiao Hailun!

718
00:39:28,616 --> 00:39:29,817
Are you in there?

719
00:39:31,377 --> 00:39:31,897
Qiao Hailun!

720
00:39:35,417 --> 00:39:36,016
Qiao Hailun!

721
00:39:36,377 --> 00:39:36,977
Qiao Hailun!

722
00:39:37,096 --> 00:39:38,937
- Qiao Hailun!
- Qiao Hailun!

723
00:39:40,496 --> 00:39:42,096
- Qiao Hailun!
- Qiao Hailun!

724
00:39:42,184 --> 00:39:44,377
(Working hard during the day
preparing presentations.)

725
00:39:44,377 --> 00:39:45,704
- (Flirting and acting cute.)
- (If it happens again, you're out!)

726
00:39:45,704 --> 00:39:47,688
- (Born a girl, she must still do this.)
- (Men buy this.)

727
00:39:53,857 --> 00:39:55,400
If the security guard hadn't told me,

728
00:39:55,576 --> 00:39:57,536
I wouldn't know you had
stayed here for so long.

729
00:39:59,297 --> 00:40:00,056
You can't do so.

730
00:40:01,377 --> 00:40:03,737
Go home now.

731
00:40:06,056 --> 00:40:08,176
But I still have two reports
I haven't finished.

732
00:40:08,377 --> 00:40:09,777
Forget about the reports.

733
00:40:09,777 --> 00:40:11,016
You need some sleep.

734
00:40:11,056 --> 00:40:13,576
Other people are busy too,
but they don't do this like you.

735
00:40:14,536 --> 00:40:15,136
Look at you,

736
00:40:16,656 --> 00:40:19,457
how could you sleep in the storage room?

737
00:40:19,937 --> 00:40:22,337
If this got out, you are putting
the company in a bad light.

738
00:40:22,937 --> 00:40:25,656
No matter what, just go home

739
00:40:26,536 --> 00:40:27,377
and get some sleep.

740
00:40:27,377 --> 00:40:28,176
I'll call a cab.

741
00:40:32,777 --> 00:40:33,704
I want to see Mr. Li.

742
00:40:41,176 --> 00:40:41,777
Li Dongming?

743
00:40:43,777 --> 00:40:45,777
If you want to see him,
you have his number,

744
00:40:45,777 --> 00:40:46,977
just call him yourself.

745
00:40:51,536 --> 00:40:54,096
I want to talk to him in person.

746
00:40:56,377 --> 00:40:58,576
I know he's in the office.

747
00:41:06,937 --> 00:41:08,016
I can call him for you,

748
00:41:08,817 --> 00:41:09,977
but no matter what'll happen,

749
00:41:10,297 --> 00:41:12,777
you have to promise me
you'll go home and sleep.

750
00:41:26,777 --> 00:41:29,377
Dongming, do you have a minute?

751
00:41:29,536 --> 00:41:30,496
Come to my office.

752
00:41:31,937 --> 00:41:33,056
Someone wants to see you.

753
00:41:35,417 --> 00:41:36,457
You'll know then.

754
00:41:38,696 --> 00:41:39,496
Okay, I'll be here.

755
00:41:47,257 --> 00:41:48,016
Thank you.

756
00:41:49,777 --> 00:41:50,417
Thank you.

757
00:42:04,562 --> 00:42:09,302
♪All the stars are out tonight♪

758
00:42:13,752 --> 00:42:15,672
♪Too much of shame♪

759
00:42:16,018 --> 00:42:18,814
♪To waste it crying♪

760
00:42:21,272 --> 00:42:23,192
♪Leave all behind you♪

761
00:42:23,192 --> 00:42:25,472
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

762
00:42:25,592 --> 00:42:27,821
♪You know how far you've gone♪

763
00:42:27,956 --> 00:42:30,232
♪In the fire you rise again♪

764
00:42:30,418 --> 00:42:32,778
♪You made it through the worst♪

765
00:42:32,916 --> 00:42:35,120
♪The best is yet to come♪

766
00:42:35,363 --> 00:42:37,503
♪The best is yet to come♪

767
00:42:40,205 --> 00:42:41,528
♪Isn't it magical♪

768
00:42:41,528 --> 00:42:43,160
♪Listen, look,
how beautiful the night is♪

769
00:42:43,192 --> 00:42:45,659
♪With countless lights on,
is someone heartbroken again♪

770
00:42:45,659 --> 00:42:48,112
♪The sound of a heart
shattering on the ground is so crisp♪

771
00:42:48,193 --> 00:42:50,841
♪Turn on a light.
A lonely heart needs comfort♪

772
00:42:50,930 --> 00:42:53,461
♪Sweat, toil, dawn, dusk♪

773
00:42:53,541 --> 00:42:55,763
♪Devaluing self-respect
just for some hot food♪

774
00:42:55,905 --> 00:42:56,986
♪But I don't want to♪

775
00:42:57,095 --> 00:42:59,361
♪Sell dignity at a price,
trampling on past vows♪

776
00:42:59,477 --> 00:43:00,542
♪Until 3 AM♪

777
00:43:00,713 --> 00:43:01,918
♪Locking dreams away in a drawer♪

778
00:43:02,072 --> 00:43:03,305
♪Just to earn some meager profit♪

779
00:43:03,396 --> 00:43:05,760
♪No matter how hard I try,
it only brings sobs♪

780
00:43:05,907 --> 00:43:10,317
♪Renewing yearly, gone with no return,
teetering, utterly bland♪

781
00:43:25,042 --> 00:43:26,478
♪Leave all behind you♪

782
00:43:26,582 --> 00:43:29,069
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

783
00:43:29,252 --> 00:43:31,381
♪You know how far you've gone♪

784
00:43:31,568 --> 00:43:33,908
♪In the fire you rise again♪

785
00:43:33,976 --> 00:43:36,242
♪You made it through the worst♪

786
00:43:36,602 --> 00:43:38,680
♪The best is yet to come♪

787
00:43:38,929 --> 00:43:41,099
♪The best is yet to come♪

788
00:43:43,800 --> 00:43:44,952
♪Isn't it magical♪

789
00:43:44,952 --> 00:43:48,598
♪All the stars are out tonight♪

790
00:43:48,632 --> 00:43:50,488
♪And I see them sparkling♪

791
00:43:50,712 --> 00:43:52,843
♪Nobody knows♪

792
00:43:53,464 --> 00:43:55,374
♪What tomorrow brings♪

793
00:43:55,640 --> 00:43:57,963
♪You made it through the worst♪

794
00:43:58,150 --> 00:44:00,358
♪The best is yet to come♪

795
00:44:00,645 --> 00:44:02,794
♪The best is yet to come♪

796
00:44:03,090 --> 00:44:04,504
♪Isn't it magical♪

797
00:44:04,504 --> 00:44:06,716
♪Feeling uneasy,
yet no one's chasing me♪

798
00:44:06,790 --> 00:44:09,144
♪Retreating step by step,
everything turning to ash♪

799
00:44:09,144 --> 00:44:10,232
♪I'm silent, I'm roaring♪

800
00:44:10,232 --> 00:44:13,683
♪This helplessness
keeps pushing me towards the cliff♪

801
00:44:14,136 --> 00:44:16,410
♪Trembling legs
carry away a shattered soul♪

802
00:44:16,824 --> 00:44:17,688
♪Who wants to be just a passerby♪

803
00:44:17,688 --> 00:44:19,208
♪Isn't it magical♪
